{
  "stem": "13382.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 25.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So going home and I said-- again, to the mother, I'd like to talk to you about something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, she was always expecting something from me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I talked to her about my strong feeling.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think it was a passionate feeling in some way, too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't-- can't live here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't stay here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I need to-- an identity.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I need to do something with myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm going aliyah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm going to Israel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she said, what about me?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, the same story as was always.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said, Mom.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Have you heard this story so many times?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If you've got to go, you got to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I promise you that I will never leave you in my mind.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The first opportunity which will occur, I'll have you join me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I've got to go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then she said somehow that Frank, who was in a-- in another town-- in Kosice.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was in a religious, sort of a youth aliyah group.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He wants to go, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, if you go, I think I'll let Frank go too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But you promise that you look after him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, of course I will.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that was sort of just the part when the-- the pre-actions.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I came home, and I had to leave about two or three hours time, the train leaves.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And nothing was packed because always usually my mother do all these things.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Mother sort of objected to do anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Something was in her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I packed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And some-- some help I got from my mother and we packed all these things together.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we walked to the station.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was-- wasn't so far in Lucenec.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she looked at me, that sadness, that pain that I saw in my mother's face.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
